platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Ride it like you built it

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: No mere port of a pre-existing classic, this is a stunning reimagining of perhaps our most beloved business-building sim. We love snagging new card packs to build bigger and better rides, and our inner Walt Disney obsesses over the perfect placement of attractions, restaurants, and, of course, restroomsyou never know when a customer is going to find one of our roller coaster creations a little too intense.
